Entry.Name: Hardware Interrupt Counter
Entry.Comment:
When Auto-Acknowledge is enabled it indicates the number of process alarms. Otherwise it shows only that an alarm has occured.
Write on object 0x5000:6 to reset the counter or to acknwoledge the alarm respectively.

Entry.Name: Diagnostic Interrupt Counter
Entry.Comment:
When Auto-Acknowledge is enabled it indicates the number of diagnostic alarms. Otherwise it shows only that an alarm has occured.
Write on object 0x5002:6 to reset the counter or to acknwoledge the alarm respectively.
